  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a cleric, you gain the following class features.</p>\n<h5>Hit Points</h5>\n<p><strong>Hit Dice:</strong> 1d8 per cleric level</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong> 18 + your Constitution modifier</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Points at Higher Levels:</strong> 1d8 (or 5) + your Constitution modifier per cleric level after 1st</p>\n<h5>Proficiencies</h5>\n<p><strong>Armor:</strong> Light armor, medium armor</p>\n<p><strong>Weapons:</strong> Simple weapons</p>\n<p><strong>Tools:</strong> None</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throws:</strong> Wisdom, Charisma</p>\n<p><strong>Skills:</strong> Choose any two from History, Insight, Medicine, Persuasion, and Religion</p>\n<h5>Equipment</h5>\n<p>You start one of the following equipment options, in addition to the equipment granted by your background:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Scale mail, a medium shield, four handaxes, and a priest's pack*</li>\n<li>A chain shirt, a maul, and a priest's pack* (if proficient with martial weapons)</li>\n<li>Ring mail, a medium shield, four handaxes, and a priest's pack* (if proficient with heavy armor)</li>\n<li>Ring mail, a medium shield, a morningstar, a priest's pack*, and 5 gp (if proficient with heavy armor and martial weapons)</li>\n<li>100 gp worth of equipment and an equipment pack</li>\n</ul>",
      "chat": "",
      "unidentified": ""
    },
